This paper discusses technical solutions for airdrops of Ethereum-based tokens, which involves issues related to resource usage, storage, and communication. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Programming Languages (cs.PL).
